[normal]              
[normal]We can talk about HIE, but 
[normal]I have to say that one of the issues is how we apply state aid and whether we should be applying it at all, rather than whether the advice from HIE 
[normal]was good or bad. That could be
[normal] “H
[normal]e said, she said” 
[normal]all day. There is an issue surrounding
[normal] whether state aid should be applied at all.
