[normal]Q155 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Sir James Paice:[bold] That is the point we are really trying to get to here. It is not just 
[normal]for, in your case, 
[normal]the forestry example that you represent
[normal],
[normal] but 
[normal]for 
[normal]the wider issues as well. I appreciate that we have now been joined by Mr Dutton from
[normal] DTAS and Mr Ritch from the Lottery—he introduced himself earlier
